{"TopicId":155895,"ForumId":55,"TopicTitle":"You should be able to lock certain positions of solar/radiator panels","CreatedByName":"JacobJHC","CreatedById":152333,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-02-02T14:42:59Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"JacobJHC","CreatedById":152333,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-02-02T14:42:59Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI have been in several situations in the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vehicle Assembly Building\u0022\u003EVAB\u003C/abbr\u003E where I have to move a large solar panel because it\u0027s rotation would clip other parts. I think it you could lock the rotation/position of solar panels it would allow for more customization options. For example, it the large solar or radiator panels could be locked, they could be used as doors for larger crafts.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/172548-notpol/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022172548\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/172548-notpol/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@/not/pol/\u003C/a\u003E pointed out that they can be locked but I think it should be something to work with inside the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vehicle Assembly Building\u0022\u003EVAB\u003C/abbr\u003E and not in the game\u0027s settings.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-02-02T14:50:30Z\u0022 title=\u002202/02/2017 02:50  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EFebruary 2, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by JacobJHC\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"/not/pol/","CreatedById":172548,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-02-02T14:48:00Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nthey already can be. in flight turn of solar tracking. inconvenient sure but it works.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"JacobJHC","CreatedById":152333,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-02-02T14:49:42Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222942245\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022155895\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221486046880\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022172548\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022/not/pol/\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 minute ago, /not/pol/ said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nthey already can be. in flight turn of solar tracking. inconvenient sure but it works.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks, I\u0027ll update the suggestion.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"natsirt721","CreatedById":117557,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-02-02T15:09:32Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo, something like and angle limiter slider in the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vehicle Assembly Building\u0022\u003EVAB\u003C/abbr\u003E? Could be nice. \u00A0Would impact radiator performance, but I can definitely see the advantages especially for the XL and 3x2 panels.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Guest","CreatedById":-1,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-02-10T06:43:33Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222942245\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022155895\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221486046880\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022172548\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022/not/pol/\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 2017/2/2 at 10:48 PM, /not/pol/ said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nthey already can be. in flight turn of solar tracking. inconvenient sure but it works.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDoes\u00A0this option exist in ksp 1.2.2? I can\u0027t find it.....\u00A0but using the \u0022tweakable everything\u0022 mod can certainly\u00A0disable solar tracking.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-02-10T06:46:22Z\u0022 title=\u002202/10/2017 06:46  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EFebruary 10, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by Guest\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"/not/pol/","CreatedById":172548,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-02-11T22:27:33Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222950664\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022155895\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221486709013\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022174796\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022whwraul7\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 2/10/2017 at 1:43 AM, whwraul7 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDoes\u00A0this option exist in ksp 1.2.2? I can\u0027t find it.....\u00A0but using the \u0022tweakable everything\u0022 mod can certainly\u00A0disable solar tracking.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYep im an idiot. i\u0027ve always used Tweakable everything so its became a \u0022Stock\u0022 option for me.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}